    "Addressing the matter requires precisely delineating the boundaries of generative artificial intelligence's knowledge base, empowering educators to fully grasp the capabilities and limitations of these tools.",
    "By understanding where LLMs excel and where they underperform, teachers can strategically incorporate these technologies into the curriculum, fostering an environment where critical thinking is encouraged.",
    "This evaluation is not just about identifying the current state of LLM technology; it's about ensuring that educators are equipped to integrate AI in a manner that complements and enhances teaching methods, rather than undermining them.",
    "While the focus of our study primarily revolves around the application of GAI in chemistry education, we recognize the importance of benchmark evaluations and performance analysis in understanding the capabilities of different models.",
    "The establishment of benchmarks is pivotal for evaluating the performance and capabilities of LLMs across a wide spectrum of tasks and domains."
